Manufacturing of some valuable products: Manufacturing of valuable products 
involve a number of chemical processes. The process is designed to produce a desired product from a variety of starting raw materials using energy through a succession of treatment steps integrated in a rational fashion (Figure 3.1). The treatment steps could be either physical or chemical in nature.

